<div>
	<div>
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">For installations requiring hazardous area certification, the hazardous area TFX Ultra transmitters with AC line power or Ethernet communications remain on hold. These transmitters are expected to be released in late February, pending certification approval.</span></div>
