		&nbsp;</div>
	<div>
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">As previously communicated, transmitters with general safety certification are available including the new AC line powered and DC powered options. If you have any open orders that need to be converted from hazardous area approval to general safety or another alternative, please contact your Badger Meter representative to revise your orders.</span></div>
